# Wisp Design

- Source of truth: design-system/wisp/MASTER.md
- Use shadcn semantic tokens: bg-background, text-muted-foreground, border-border
- Status colors via CSS variables: --status-running, --status-success, --status-neutral
- Dark-first; no raw Tailwind colors (bg-blue-500) for UI chrome
- Use flex gap-* not space-y-*; cn() for conditional classes
- Lucide icons only; cursor-pointer on clickable elements; 150-300ms transitions
